CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Full length portrait of woman, possibly Aileen Eckstein Sawyer, wearing light colored evening gown with single strap over right shoulder, posed in front light colored curtains in interior with patterned carpeting, for Thirtieth Anniversary of Girl Friends, Inc.
